ANALYTICSD(8) System Manager's Manual ANALYTICSD(8)

NAME

analyticsd —
Diagnostics and Usage

SYNOPSIS

analyticsd

DESCRIPTION

analyticsd is a system daemon that collects diagnostics and usage data locally for users that have opted in.

There are no configuration options to analyticsd, and users should not run analyticsd manually.

SEE ALSO

brctl(1)
